experience.title: Data Analyst
bullets: Designed and implemented 5 Python scripts for data cleaning, preprocessing, and analysis, improving data pipeline efficiency by 30%, processing 100K records weekly.

Leveraged AI techniques to automate 4 repetitive tasks, reducing manual effort by 20% and improving overall productivity.
Built 6 dynamic dashboards and visualizations using Python libraries like Matplotlib and Seaborn to communicate insights effectively, enhancing stakeholder engagement.
Integrated Google Analytics data with Python for advanced analysis, enhancing customer behavior insights by 40%.

experience.title: Data Analyst
bullets: Automated data extraction and structuring of 10 population datasets using Python, improving data accuracy by 35% and team collaboration.
Analyzed customer support data with Python to optimize response times by 20% and enhance operational efficiency.

Designed 3 Python scripts to create dynamic reports and dashboards, significantly improving customer satisfaction by 30% and decision-making processes.

experience.title: Software Engineer and Analyst
bullets: Built 5 Python scripts to track key metrics, ensuring 99% data accuracy and improving data integrity and operational efficiency.
Collaborated with a team of 4 to enhance analytics capabilities, using Python to improve data processing speed by 25%.
Leveraged Python for data preprocessing and analysis, producing 3 Tableau dashboards that improved decision-making.
Supported cross-functional teams with Python-driven insights, enabling 5 customer-focused initiatives.

experience.title: Research Assistant
bullets: Utilized advanced Python programming for computational modeling and solving complex research problems across 3 projects.

experience.title: Lecturer and Course Facilitator
bullets: Led engaging physics tutorials for 20 master’s students, enhancing understanding and promoting teamwork.

Mentored students on 10 projects, collaborated with faculty, and fostered student engagement.

bullets: Developed proficiency in Python programming by researching the effect of magnetic fields on 2D materials.
Managed and analyzed complex data sets, improving their accuracy and reliability by 25%.
Used Power BI to present research findings and participated in weekly reviews, improving collaboration and research skills.
